{"tid":1892253,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警務督察涉嫌襲擊前女友　被控普通襲擊、遊蕩及拒捕","createTime":"2020-02-22T11:45:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-25T13:29:48.000Z","uid":125168,"like":371,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":77,"replies":[{"pid":"9eb8386ba09ac04e269ac8571f90745e3da61416","tid":1892253,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T11:45:52.000Z","msg":"警務督察涉嫌襲擊前女友　被控普通襲擊、遊蕩及拒捕　候取兩份精神科報告2020/02/22 19:19<br />\n【有線新聞】一名警務督察涉嫌襲擊前女友，被控普通襲擊、遊蕩及拒捕，案件押後至下月初，被告還押小欖，等候索取兩份精神科報告。<br />\n<br />\n35歲被告李天洛，被控於去年8月在長沙灣襲擊前女友。控方指二人前年分手後，被告多次前往對方屋企，之後自殺不遂，確診患上抑鬱症。其後再登門找前女友遭拒絕，並在附近遊蕩。女方全家搬屋後，被告多次到她工作地點。被告昨日在葵芳被捕，另外他涉嫌在黃竹坑襲擊另一名女子。他毋須答辯，並拒絕由當值律師對答，申請保釋亦被拒。"},{"pid":"48bdbf593e46d65f3e88c0bfbdc829636e4db4dd","tid":1892253,"uid":125168,"like":170,"dislike":0,"score":170,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T11:46:37.000Z","msg":"估下判幾多個鐘社會服務令？定扮痴線所以咩後果都無？"},{"pid":"24b67aa637cd84bbb818d739e722b54a884e2667","tid":1892253,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T11:48:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"015b1be74b6a49a39d26f521d9720f304a27c35b","tid":1892253,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T11:49:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfde2a8b08142e4e1e2602d93b34feb3093f9cb6","tid":1892253,"uid":165749,"like":137,"dislike":0,"score":137,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T11:50:08.000Z","msg":"警世，好女唔做狗閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a23fe682cd5df0a8e95e891f12f2af5ddcf6cb5","tid":1892253,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T11:51:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9791e497aef05d8f2f2b119058ac88449b815f62","tid":1892253,"uid":196924,"like":54,"dislike":8,"score":46,"citedBy":12,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T11:51:49.000Z","msg":"成35歲都仲係督察?<br />\n好多三十頭都升