"cd8d145dfc3ac2c83a5634e4903d07cf1a79c79b","tid":1892253,"uid":271617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"48bdbf593e46d65f3e88c0bfbdc829636e4db4dd","tid":1892253,"uid":125168,"like":170,"dislike":0,"score":170,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T11:46:37.000Z","msg":"估下判幾多個鐘社會服務令？定扮痴線所以咩後果都無？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T14:51:08.000Z","msg":"180小時"},{"pid":"8da16f14cbba7348cfa02be6f9a54f62d175add8","tid":1892253,"uid":58604,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0d649df58bac8094c797db07e5b1a3af067c46aa","tid":1892253,"uid":121197,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T12:24:41.000Z","msg":"條友好好笑<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">被告今日上庭時，拒絕聘用當值律師，選擇自行陳詞。主任裁判官錢禮見被告以英語表達時未見流暢，一度詢問他是否需要翻譯協助。惟被告堅持可於庭上自行與眾人對答。<br />\n控方申請將案件押後，先為被告索取兩份精神科報告，再考慮被告是否適合答辯，同時反對被告保釋候訊。被告要求擔保外出，又自言不介意控方為其索取精神科報告；但若未能保釋，則拒絕還押小欖。據了解，被告去年9月曾在私家車內企圖燒炭自殺，其後被送往葵涌精神病院，留醫四星期，其後須到精神科復診。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200222/HTGKDWUYD52OKSS2GWTXG3VHNM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200222%2FHTGKDWUYD52OKSS2GWTXG3VHNM%2F&d=l2jL6rfoxymyXK22uA%2BdgtqeVONt7zbw7GHn8%2FjWPdo%3D&h=01eaf07a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200222%2FHTGKDWUYD52OKSS2GWTXG3VHNM%2F&h=a29c26f9\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200222/HTGKDWUYD52OKSS2GWTXG3VHNM/</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T14:52:01.000Z","msg":"私家車內燒炭自殺呢下<br />\n唔比少少智商都諗唔到<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91396f4e1cd97dff61b31f6d1024edd62ae7bbc0","tid":1892253,"uid":335434,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"9791e497aef05d8f2f2b119058ac88449b815f62","tid":1892253,"uid":196924,"like":54,"dislike":8,"score":46,"citedBy":12,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T11:51:49.000Z","msg":"成35歲都仲係督察?<br />\n好多三十頭都升三粒花啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T14:54:20.000Z","msg":"原來呢條友好撚經典架<br />\n<blockquote>據了解，被告的父親是一名退休警察。翻查網上資料，被告曾於2016年接受警方刊物《警聲》訪問，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>分享晉升至督察的經歷。他當時駐守警隊，並於2012年晉升為見習督察，進入警校接受訓練。惟他在結業前一個月，其中兩份試卷不合格，需要終止訓練並回復警員職級。</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n他自言這是前所未有的打擊，亦動搖了他的信心。但其後他許下承諾，決定再次投考督察，「在那兒倒下，便得在那兒站起來」。他明白讀書是他最弱一環，遂利用公餘時間進修英文、溫習警例和鍛鍊體能，最終通過所有考試，於2016年2月畢業。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢係做咗6年老散考到入班做幫辦 <br />\n跟住入到去學堂臨畢業考試肥佬燉返做老散 <br />\n落返去做多幾年老散再考入去多次先成功畢業做督察 <br />\n<br />\n明明讀書廢EQ低 咁撚辛苦先躝到上去 但為咗部公家水炮車就痴撚咗線由白衫sir變白卡佬 難怪平時咁多白卡周街跳掣發癲 原來升咗咁多垃圾老散痴線佬上去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nbtw 連上庭講兩句英文都俾個官串叫佢搵傳譯 入幫辦班考試衰過都仲可以再入多次 睇黎佢升上去背後都有好多污糟邋遢嘢架喇"},{"pid":"cf5aea57ad767591de5fc08f1233c2171a9cc36c","tid":1892253,"uid":136689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4a84d523e787e4106d890c658fa1a42b70ac9216","tid":1892253,"uid":73853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"86e3f7db5309e095a1bb48ed8527a7065524cfe8","tid":1892253,"uid":136689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9ef9d21a6600f16e6011b01e34758b8fd4bdead2","tid":1892253,"uid":46042,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T12:00:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T12:37:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T14:32:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T15:07:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec6cecc20f8a3e2f950a85f1a9f0d274d8f026a4","tid":1892253,"uid":73853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cf5aea57ad767591de5fc08f1233c2171a