02-22T13:19:22.000Z","msg":"警察都有fast track既<br />\n最top既40頭~40中就總警司 (erer狗同謝振中)<br />\n38、39就高級警司<br />\n35、36就警司<br />\n30頭三粒花<br />\n但大多數30頭都係高級督察黎<br />\n30尾40頭先會總督察，然後一係封頂一係再升<br />\n<br />\n而如果見到d廢中廢老只係督察<br />\n應該係經警署警長推薦計劃升職<br />\n依班人多數督察/高級督察退休"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T14:17:48.000Z","msg":"好似警署警長都唔易升<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n光頭狗都有番咁上下料"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T14:24:22.000Z","msg":"大約1:5左右<br />\n唔算難都唔算易"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T15:41:36.000Z","msg":"其實時沙係差館做咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n聽大學同學係狗屋做過煙腸<br />\n話時沙返去蛇王打機"},{"pid":"41ef5cc754e2d8bbb214699fe560cf9a0580db13","tid":1892253,"uid":14449,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"341a5f71abc1e7405a5103da7b9b5e7a12a44ae1","tid":1892253,"uid":55458,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"9791e497aef05d8f2f2b119058ac88449b815f62","tid":1892253,"uid":196924,"like":54,"dislike":8,"score":46,"citedBy":12,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T11:51:49.000Z","msg":"成35歲都仲係督察?<br />\n好多三十頭都升三粒花啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T14:34:31.000Z","msg":"邊有咁多三粒花<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T15:43:02.000Z","msg":"呢件由散仔開始升<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n30歲3粒算升好快"},{"pid":"8cae3f3c86309bf7bf58e9824ad6f46902bbccc1","tid":1892253,"uid":126317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3f4abbfb6fdec1891a4a8b2ff9e07af600b35c8a","tid":1892253,"uid":121459,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T12:13:37.000Z","msg":"睇成蟲大哥學返黎既係咁上下啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T15:53:39.000Z","msg":"如果搞大個肚，連自己條精蟲都唔敢認"},{"pid":"e50df3292f39a766137e6f6db1d40487814114bc","tid":1892253,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T15:53:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"093cd475259c6